    "can be found in ref. 10.",
    "To widen the scope of the generated synthetic theorems and proofs, we also introduce another component to the symbolic engine that can deduce new statements through algebraic rules (AR), as described in Methods.",
    "AR is necessary to perform angle, ratio and distance chasing, as often required in many olympiadlevel proofs.",
    "We included concrete examples of AR in Extended Data Table 2.",
    "The combination DD + AR, which includes both their forward deduction and traceback algorithms, is a new contribution in our work and represents a new state of the art in symbolic reasoning in geometry."
